<br>
Sontalak, I don't agree with.  The mob has lost seemingly all semblence of strategy, and with only 90k hp, he's become a Zerg-type mob.  I would think TON stands a better chance of killing him than TWC, or any other guild at this time, because they have an insane wizard force for this type of battle, yet I don't think ToN is the #3 guild.<br>
<br>
I'm not blasting ToN or anything, I've been impressed as hell with them lately, I was pretty certain that the guild's fallout was going to cripple them, instead they seem to have gotten stronger.<br>
<br>
But on the other hand, I think you are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> dead on target</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> with the Aary thoery.  In my opinion, the first guild to clear him and thus NToV, will have taken a huge step over anyone just @#%$ around with First Brood.  But mobilization to get a chance at him will be near impossible with OOP and HnE havine so many powerful members than can be called upon whenever needed...<br>
