<br>
Ancient Council in my opinion is the best of those guilds though.   While they have never been the most powerful and are just now coming into their own, their history shows what their future will be.   AC has been around for a long time and has never once had a large falling out or a leader change.   They have constantly grown as a family and will probably continue to grow and eventually become one of the top powers.<br>
<br>
Of course on our server we have unique guild relationships.   While we do have alot of fights over all we are one of the calmest servers from the guild politics point of view.  Many guilds team up and kill mobs that they could not do without the others.   Because of this it is hard to tell who will become the next uber guild but I guarantee it will take a guild with strong relationships with other guilds of the same power now. <p><Font size="-1" color="green"><u>Caan</u><BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90906">58 Dark Elf Ranger<BR><A HREF="http://www.titansofsaryrn.com">Titans of Saryrn</a>
